description:
(Found in Collection, 8/9/95)
Necklace of dark grey stone beads with four evenly spaced larger beads and two larger beads at end; end section is double stranded; top bead in end section has three carved circles and slanted lines; Two tags '586' and 'B-586 (Record Book)'; also had tag 'R.B. no I.D. # problem 93'.
title: Necklace of Dark Grey Stone with Four Evenly Spaced Beads
